title: TranRantic 4Pcs Travel Laundry Bag, Waterproof Laundry Bag Dirty Clothes, 3 Sizes Wet Bags for Swimming Yoga Workout, Foldable Laundry Bags for Travelling Family Vacation (Blue)
features: 【High-quality materials】This laundry bag is made from ribbed Nylon fabric, which has excellent abrasion resistance and tear strength, which is not only strong, but also effectively prevents moisture penetration, ensuring isolation between wet and dry clothes, so that the clothes can be transported safely and protected from moisture in other contents.

【Various sizes】The set contains four well-designed waterproof travel bags measuring 60cm× 45cm, 55cm×35cm and two 20cm×20cm. Whether it's a large piece of clothing, a small piece of personal items, or children's clothing, you'll find the right storage space. When you're not in use, these laundry bags can be easily folded into a compact size for easy storage in your suitcase or closet without taking up too much space, making your trip a great convenience.

【Portable Design】The dirty clothes travel bag is equipped with a special loop closure and smooth zipper to make it easy to carry and hang clothes. The handle on the side is cleverly designed, so you can easily pick up your clothes and even hang them anywhere. The metal zipper is durable and glides smoothly to avoid fabric damage, ensuring safety and convenience during use. When it comes to cleaning and maintenance, simply wipe the surface with a damp cloth and avoid direct cleaning to protect its special coating.

【Personalized Selection】While pursuing practicality, travel laundry bags also focus on aesthetics. They come in bright colors as well as delicate details, and you can choose different colors of laundry bags according to your personal preferences and needs to meet your personalized use needs. Whether you're looking for practicality or style, you'll find a satisfying choice in these laundry bags.

【Perfect Travel Companion】These waterproof laundry bags are not only a great helper for daily household washing, but also an ideal companion for travel, camping, fitness and swimming enthusiasts. They manage dirty laundry efficiently and avoid mix-ups, whether you're loading dirty laundry, swimsuits or gym clothes. At the same time, these laundry bags are breathable to keep air circulating and prevent unpleasant odours from developing, keeping clothes fresh and natural.
